OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FThe first weekend of campaigning is
OL,7,Fset to get under way in Makerfield, in
OL,8,Fa by-election that Andy Burnham said
OL,9,Fcould "change Labour".
OL,11,FMr Burnham, who is viewed as a
OL,12,Fchallenger to Sir Keir Starmer in a
OL,13,Fpotential Labour leadership race,
OL,14,Flaunched his by-election campaign on
OL,15,FFriday and promised he was not
OL,16,Foffering "more of the same".
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@UO]xD@JOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
