CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779584596
OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FAllies of Mr Burnham have suggested he
OL,7,Fmay not launch a bid for the party
OL,8,Fleadership immediately if he is
OL,9,Fsuccessful in his attempt to return to
OL,10,FParliament in the June 18 contest.
OL,12,FBut Wes Streeting, who resigned from
OL,13,Fthe Cabinet earlier this month, has
OL,14,Fopenly talked about launching a
OL,15,Fcampaign to oust Prime Minister Sir
OL,16,FKeir.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779584596
OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FThe MP and former health secretary
OL,7,Ftold reporters on Friday that he held
OL,8,Foff triggering a leadership race to
OL,9,Fgive Mr Burnham time to tread a path
OL,10,Fback into the Commons.
OL,12,FIn a pitch to voters, Greater
OL,13,FManchester Mayor Mr Burnham said: "I
OL,14,Fknow my own party needs to change. We
OL,15,Fneed to be better than we have been.
OL,17,F"A vote for me in this by-election is
OL,18,Fa vote to change Labour."
OL,26,@uD@cOUyD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779584596
OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FMr Burnham, who is also a former
OL,7,Fhealth secretary, later told reporters
OL,8,FLabour has "space to be more radical"
OL,9,Fwhile honouring the party's 2024
OL,10,Fgeneral election manifesto.
OL,12,FThis could include council tax
OL,13,Freforms, targeting the construction of
OL,14,Fmore council houses, considering the
OL,15,Fabolition of inheritance tax and
OL,16,Fbringing in a care levy.
OL,18,FHe also said he thought the Government
OL,19,Fwas "moving in the right direction" on
OL,20,Fimmigration but suggested ministers
OL,21,Fshould consult on the proposals.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@eO]{D@EOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
