OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779584596
OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FMr Kenyon was joined on the campaign
OL,7,Ftrail earlier this week by his party
OL,8,Fleader, Nigel Farage.
OL,10,FThe Liberal Democrats unveiled
OL,11,FStockport councillor Jake Austin as
OL,12,Ftheir candidate to contest the seat,
OL,13,Fwho said voters in Makerfield "deserve
OL,14,Fso much more than the failing Labour
OL,15,FGovernment or the divisive politics of
OL,16,FReform UK".
OL,26,@uD@_OUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
