OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FThe Conservatives have named Michael
OL,7,FWinstanley as their candidate, while
OL,8,Fthe Greens on Thursday named Chris
OL,9,FKennedy, who withdrew from the race
OL,10,Fshortly after his selection.
OL,12,FThe party said Mr Kennedy had
OL,13,Fwithdrawn for "personal and family
OL,14,Freasons", but it later emerged that he
OL,15,Fhad shared posts on social media
OL,16,Fclaiming an attack on Jewish
OL,17,Fambulances in north London had been a
OL,18,F"false flag" operation.
OL,26,@uD@OOUvD@HO]zD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779584596
OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FA Green spokesperson said Mr Kennedy
OL,7,Fhad deleted and apologised for the
OL,8,Fposts, but added the party stood by
OL,9,Fits previous statement about the
OL,10,Freasons for his withdrawal.
OL,12,FIn an interview with the Mirror
OL,13,Fnewspaper, Mr Streeting backed Mr
OL,14,FBurnham's campaign.
OL,16,F"We need all of our best players on
OL,17,Fthe pitch," he said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
