CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779584596
OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,F"We've obviously got the Makerfield by-
OL,7,Felection underway, where Andy Burnham
OL,8,Fhas my full support, and I suspect
OL,9,FAndy Burnham would want to be a
OL,10,Fcandidate in a leadership race.
OL,12,F"And I felt that if I'd rushed ahead
OL,13,Fand triggered a leadership contest
OL,14,Fbefore Andy Burnham had the chance to
OL,15,Fcome back, people would have just said
OL,16,FI was trying to pull a fast one,
OL,17,Ftrying to get ahead of the
OL,18,Fcompetition."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
