OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FMr Streeting also unveiled one of his
OL,7,F"first campaign pledges" ` to "fund
OL,8,Fthe full restoration of Sure Start".
OL,10,FThe Ilford North MP said: "It would
OL,11,Fshow that this Labour Government, and
OL,12,Fa Labour government I lead, is
OL,13,Fabsolutely committed to building a
OL,14,Fbetter future for the next generation,
OL,15,Fmaking sure that kids ` all kids ` get
OL,16,Fthe very best start in life, closing
OL,17,Fthat gap that sees kids from poorer
OL,18,Ffamilies arrive at school with their
OL,19,Ffutures already determined, already
OL,20,Fdisadvantaged from those from the more
OL,21,Fwealthier backgrounds."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@XO]oD@_OUpD@cO]rD@[OU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
