OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FHe added he would pay for the proposal
OL,7,Fwith a wealth tax, building in carve-
OL,8,Fouts for "things like entrepreneurs'
OL,9,Fallowances and investment allowances
OL,10,Fto encourage those wealth creators to
OL,11,Finvest in the sort of businesses that
OL,12,Fwill improve our growth".
OL,14,FSpeaking to the Guardian, he suggested
OL,15,Fmaking the independent Planning
OL,16,FInspectorate more involved in
OL,17,Fapproving new housing and easing some
OL,18,Fof the thresholds at which housing
OL,19,Fdevelopers must carry out an
OL,20,Fenvironmental assessment of their
OL,21,Fproposals.
OL,26,@pD@JOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
