OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779584596
OL,3,CFirst weekend of Makerfield by-
OL,4,Celection campaigns to get under way
OL,6,FHe also insisted he had the numbers to
OL,7,Flaunch a leadership bid, "including
OL,8,Fministers", before he held off
OL,9,Ftriggering one.
OL,11,FJosh Simons, the Labour MP who stood
OL,12,Fdown to make way for Mr Burnham, won
OL,13,Fin 2024 by just 5,399 votes, while
OL,14,FReform comfortably won every ward in
OL,15,Fthe constituency at this month's local
OL,16,Felections.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
